							<span>Delivery &amp; Shipping Policies</span>
						</h2>
						<hr class="x-gap" style="margin: 1.313em 0 0 0;">
						<p>
							<strong>Appeti.in&nbsp;</strong>is committed to delivering your
							order in the best possible way. We try our hardest to ensure that
							we provide the most efficient dispatch and for the same we have
							partnered with the best Logistics Service Providers that gets
							your orders to you as swiftly as possible.
						</p>
						<p>
							<strong><u>Payment Options</u></strong>
						</p>
						<p>We accept payments made using credit card, debit card and
							net banking. We accept most major Credit/Debit Cards. Pay as you
							like!</p>
						<p>
							<strong><u>Delivery Area and Timings</u></strong>
						</p>
						<p>We deliver pan-India in 1-7 business days depending upon
							customer's location. Public Holidays and Saturdays/Sundays are
							excluded from business days since we do not ship anything on
							these days to prevent the lag in shipments.</p>
						<p>Please note that the delivery timing depends on a number of
							factors like: weather, unforeseen events, traffic conditions and
							other special events. However, we will always endeavour to
							complete the delivery as early as possible and keep you updated
							in case of any changes</p>
						<p>
							<strong><u>Delivery Charges/Minimum Order</u></strong>
						</p>
						<p>Our all prices are inclusive of all taxes, packaging and
							shipping cost. There are no hidden charges for delivery.</p>
						<p>
							<strong><u>What if the product is received in
									damaged condition?</u></strong>
						</p>
						<p>In case of complaints regarding foods that come with a
							warranty from Brand Owners, please refer the issue to the
							concerned Brand Owner. Let us know; we'll help you regarding the
							same.</p>
						<p>
							If you think, you have received the food items in a bad condition
							or if the packaging is tampered with or damaged before
							delivery,&nbsp;please email us at&nbsp;<strong><a
								href="mailto:${headerBean.email}">${headerBean.email}</a></strong>&nbsp;mentioning
							your Order ID within 24 hours of accepting the package. We will
							request you for the pictures of the shipment and individual
							pictures of the boxes which will be provided to the Food Vendors
							and the courier partner within 48 hours of shipment delivery. If
							the claim is genuine as found by us, the Food Vendor and the
							Courier Partner,&nbsp;<strong>we will get the shipment
								picked back and initiate exchange or refund for the same.</strong>
						</p>
